com.javadocking.dock.factory
Class TabDockFactory

java.lang.Object
  com.javadocking.dock.factory.TabDockFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
DockFactory
public class TabDockFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements DockFactory

This dock factory creates a TabDock if the given dockable has DockingMode.TAB as one of its possible docking modes.

When the dockable cannot be added to a tab dock, the creation of the dock can be delegated to an alternative dock factory. If this factory is null, then null will be returned.

Author:
Heidi Rakels
